'''Ancient Megalodon''' is an {{Rarity|Exotic}} fish found in the [[Ancient Isle]].

== Description ==
{{Description|The Ancient Megalodon is a colossal predatory shark from prehistoric times, unmatched in size and ferocity. With its massive mouth and serrated teeth, it can effortlessly rip through any obstacle. A true apex predator of the Ancient Isle, it offers an incredible battle for those daring to catch it.|Bestiary Entry}}

